OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1783792086
OL,3,CMan charged with murder of missing
OL,4,Cmother last seen in 1998
OL,6,FA man has been charged with the murder
OL,7,Fof a mother-of-seven from Dudley who
OL,8,Fwent missing in 1998.
OL,10,FPatricia Lashley, known to her friends
OL,11,Fas Pat or Jade, was 33-years-old when
OL,12,Fshe disappeared from her flat in Hall
OL,13,FStreet.
OL,15,FTrevor Dunkley, 66, has been charged
OL,16,Fwith murder in connection with her
OL,17,Fdisappearance almost 30 years ago.
OL,19,FMs Lashley also used the names Vanessa
OL,20,Fand Tricia as well as the surname
OL,21,FBradford.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/3
