PN,34903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1783792086
OL,3,CMan charged with murder of missing
OL,4,Cmother last seen in 1998
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Michelle Cordell
OL,7,Fsaid: "Even if you already spoke to us
OL,8,Fat the time Patricia went missing, we
OL,9,Fstill want to hear from you as we
OL,10,Fgather as much information as we can
OL,11,Fto help her family find some closure
OL,12,Fafter nearly 30 years."
OL,14,FDunkley has been remanded into custody
OL,15,Fand is due to appear at Wolverhampton
OL,16,FCrown Court on Monday 13 July.
